## Origin

ClipForge was developed by Techseria as a single-tenant AI video
generation platform for marketers. The first version was designed to
turn plain-language instructions into finished promotional videos by
orchestrating three interchangeable AI video models:

- Google Gemini Veo Pro
- Google Gemini Veo Flash
- MiniMax Hailuo 2.3

The platform addresses a real problem: marketing teams need short,
branded video content produced at scale, but most off-the-shelf
generators are tied to a single provider and produce inconsistent
output. ClipForge's value is in the workflow: project/scene model,
global style propagation, regeneration history, FFmpeg merge with
transitions, and per-user daily quota enforcement across providers.

It is released as open source under the AGPL v3 so that other
organizations facing the same problem can deploy, study, modify,
and redistribute it under terms that keep the ecosystem open.

